Package org.springframework.cli

Interface Summary
Command A single command that can be run from the CLI.
CommandFactory Factory used to create CLI Commands.
 

Class Summary
Log Simple logger used by the CLI.
SpringCli Spring Command Line Interface.
 

Enum Summary
SpringCliException.Option Specific options understood by the SpringCli.
 

Exception Summary
SpringCliException Runtime exception wrapper that defines additional SpringCliException.Options that are understood by the SpringCli.
